column2: 111, Inc. engages in the provision of pharmaceutical products and medical services through online retail pharmacy and indirectly through offline pharmacy network. The company is headquartered in Shanghai, Shanghai and currently employs 1,350 full-time employees. The firm is mainly engaged in the provision of online medical services, drug purchasing and health management services through Internet and information technology. The firm mainly conducts its business in the domestic market.
No. 295, Zuchongzhi Road, Pudong New Area
